name: anti_join
constraint: (declare-const CO_SPEC Int)(declare-const RO_SPEC Int)(declare-const CI_SPEC Int)(declare-const CI2_SPEC Int)(declare-const RI_SPEC Int)(declare-const RI2_SPEC Int)(assert (= CO_SPEC CI_SPEC))(assert (< RO_SPEC RI_SPEC))(assert (> RO_SPEC 0))

(define-sort Set () (Array Int Bool))(declare-const SET_I_SPEC (Set))(declare-const SET_I2_SPEC (Set))(declare-const SET_O_SPEC (Set))(assert (= SET_I_SPEC SET_O_SPEC))(assert (not (= (intersect SET_I2_SPEC SET_O_SPEC) ((as const Set) false))))
